<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_314_r1l18">Wır ~ dıe <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> etc Bekennen etc Als ſıch dıe <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> veſten <expan>Vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_314_r1l19">Bertlein von Swangöw <expan>gebrud<ex>er</ex></expan> . <expan>frıcʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒeſels <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> / <expan>geg<ex>en</ex></expan> vns ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_314_r1l20"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſprechen</expan> <expan>angenome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd vns von <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>geſchrıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan> daʒ ſıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_314_r1l21">Jm ʒu recht <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> vns helffen <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> / Daʒ dıe <expan>hochgeborn<ex>en</ex></expan> fürſten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_314_r1l22">vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> . <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Ernſt vnd <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> vvılhelm <expan>gebrud<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Pfallncʒgraf<ex>en</ex></expan> bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_314_r1l23">Reyn vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog<ex>en</ex></expan> in Peyern etc <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ſache <expan>ʒwıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>beıd<ex>er</ex></expan> ſeıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_314_r1l24">gütlıch <expan>abgenome<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . Alſo <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> wır der <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> von Swangow </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_314_r1l25">vnd der Jren vmb dıe <expan>obgen<ex>ante</ex></expan> ſache vnd was ſıch bıs auf dıſʒ ʒeıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_314_r1l26"><expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ergang<ex>en</ex></expan> hat gut freẅnde für vns vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_314_line_1577276698914_217">Mıt <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> etc <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſıgelt</expan> etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_314" id="156r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
