<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Wir, die <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> etc., bekennen etc., als sich die
                                <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vesten
                        <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>, und Bertlein
                        von Swangöw, <expan>gebrud<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                            <expan>Fricze<ex>n</ex></expan> Zesels, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>, <expan>geg<ex>en</ex></expan> uns zu
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sprechen</expan>
<expan>angenome<ex>n</ex></expan> und uns von <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>geschribe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz sie im zu recht
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> uns helffen
                        <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz die <expan>hochgeborn<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        fürsten und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
                        Ernst und <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Wilhelm,
                            <expan>gebrud<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>pfallnczgraf<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        bey Reyn und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan> in Peyern etc.,
                                <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> sache
                            <expan>zwische<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>beid<ex>er</ex></expan> seit gütlich
                            <expan>abgenome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Also <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> wir der
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> von Swangow und der iren umb die
                                <expan>obgen<ex>ante</ex></expan> sache und was sich bis auf disz
                        zeit <expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ergang<ex>en</ex></expan> hat gut frewnde für uns und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>.
                        Mit <expan>urk<ex>unde</ex></expan> etc. <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sigelt</expan>
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
